  "title": "Locum Renal Staff Nurse ($29/HR) #HJO",
  "description": "<p>Job Description<br /></p><ul><li>Provide safe and competent nursing care to patients undergoing haemodialysis or peritoneal dialysis.</li><li>Administer medications and intravenous therapies as prescribed in accordance with protocols.</li><li>Monitor and manage dialysis-related complications and escalate promptly when required.</li><li>Maintain strict adherence to infection control, aseptic techniques and dialysis safety standards</li></ul><p>Requirements</p><ul><li>Registered Nurse with valid registration with the Singapore Nursing Board (SNB).</li></ul><ul><li>Minimum 1–2 years of relevant renal nursing experience </li></ul><p>Interested candidates are invited to email your resume to:</p><p></p><p>jen.ooi@recruitexpress.com.sg</p><p></p><p>Jenalyn Ooi Huai Sian (R1765551)</p><p>Recruit Express Pte Ltd  | Company Reg. No. 199601303W | EA License Number: 99C4599</p><p>We regret only suitable candidates will be shortlisted for an interview.</p><p><br /></p><p><ul></ul></p>",
